<concept id="_5_1_3_budget_identify_resources">
    <title>5.1.3 Budget: Identify Resources</title>
    <shortdesc>Define what the product should look like and its functions.</shortdesc>
    <conbody>
        <p>Determine what you need to create the product - capital, people, tools? Resource
            selection impacts the product plan and roadmap. Aligning resources with needs is crucial
            for reaching your goals. A poorly defined budget can cause delays and give competitors
            an edge. Budget elements to include:</p>
        <ul id="ul_jt2_sq2_qbc">
            <li>
                <p>Staff costs</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Tools and software costs</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Material and external service costs</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Estimated total project cost</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </conbody>
</concept>
